Mapapatunayan namin ni Manager Nah iyon.

84
00:04:45.167 --> 00:04:46.767
- Tama?
- Huh? Oo.

85
00:04:46.767 --> 00:04:49.433
Nakita ng lahat kung gaano kahirap magtrabaho si Manager Jang.

86
00:04:49.433 --> 00:04:52.100
