- Halika.

135
00:08:07.733 --> 00:08:10.267
Medyo oblivious na yata ako.

136
00:08:10.267 --> 00:08:11.967
Tiyo.

137
00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.900
ha? Se Hyeon.

138
00:08:19.833 --> 00:08:21.867
Kamusta ang balikat mo?

139
00:08:21.867 --> 00:08:24.300
Okay lang, walang seryoso.

140
00:08:25.033 --> 00:08:27.033
Hindi ko alam kung bakit nagkakaganito si Mama.

141
00:08:27.033 --> 00:08:29.167
Hiyang-hiya na rin ako sa harap ni Manager.

142
00:08:29.167 --> 00:08:32.567
