Paano si Yeol Mu?

213
00:11:53.900 --> 00:11:55.500
This much will not bother me.

214
00:11:55.500 --> 00:11:57.100
Tama ba, Yeol Mu?

215
00:11:57.100 --> 00:11:59.200
Halos malagay ka sa malaking problema.

216
00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:03.267
Alam mo ba kung gaano ako natakot
